    "In this section, we will interpret these findings and their implications for understanding and mitigating the impact of disinformation.",
    "Furthermore, we will acknowledge the limitations of our study and outline prospective directions for future research in this domain.",
    "Firstly, the actors involved in disseminating disinformation are markedly more active and work intricately within their networks.",
